            <button class="quiz-opt" data-q="5" data-correct="false">D — 5-year satellites are always lighter, enabling more per launch</button>
        </div><div class="quiz-feedback" id="fb5"></div></div>

    <div class="quiz-q"><p><strong>Q6.</strong> Pre-wired electrical harness looms replace custom point-to-point wiring in mass satellite production primarily to:</p>
        <div class="quiz-options">
