            <button class="quiz-opt" data-q="6" data-correct="true">B — Eliminate the most labour-intensive step in spacecraft assembly, reducing assembly time from months to days and cutting wiring-related defects</button>
            <button class="quiz-opt" data-q="6" data-correct="false">C — Allow on-orbit repair of electrical faults</button>
            <button class="quiz-opt" data-q="6" data-correct="false">D — Reduce the satellite's total electrical mass</button>
        </div><div class="quiz-feedback" id="fb6"></div></div>

    <div class="quiz-q"><p><strong>Q7.</strong> The satellite and launch vehicle learning curves interact because:</p>
        <div class="quiz-options">
